title: Johnny Cash Live San Quentin [Video Album]
description:
Johnny Cash Live at San Quentin Prison (1969) was a ground breaking concert for many reasons, one of which was of course the fact it was allowed to go ahead in the first place.  Johnny Cash of course had been to prison himself so could definitely relate to the problems the inmates were up against.

Includes the original documentary footage after each song.

Source Granada DVD MPEG2 Edited into individual Music video's.  Sort by date/time for original track order.  720P Audio 320kbps

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
